{
  "id": "69c28107d1488f7c8d4d645e",
  "title": "元を取ろうという発想",
  "created": 1774354705,
  "updated": 1774355657,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c28107d1488f7c8d4d645e",
      "text": "元を取ろうという発想",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774354705,
      "updated": 1774354705
    },
    {
      "id": "69c281bc0000000000e5cdaf",
      "text": "[損失回避バイアス]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774354877,
      "updated": 1774354882
    },
    {
      "id": "69c281bc0000000000e5cdb0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774354877,
      "updated": 1774354877
    },
    {
      "id": "69c281100000000000e5cda8",
      "text": "逆に損するんじゃないか[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774354705,
      "updated": 1774354727
    },
    {
      "id": "69c281250000000000e5cda9",
      "text": "\t食べ放題で元を取ろうとして無理矢理腹に詰め込んで",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774354727,
      "updated": 1774354805
    },
    {
      "id": "69c281750000000000e5cdac",
      "text": " \t吐く（QOL低下）とか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774354805,
      "updated": 1774354806
    },
    {
      "id": "69c281780000000000e5cdad",
      "text": " \t気持ち悪さを抑えるために胃薬を飲む（金銭的損失）とか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774354808,
      "updated": 1774354831
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2818e0000000000e5cdae",
      "text": " \tその後の時間にやること・やりたいことができなくなる（機会損失）とか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774354831,
      "updated": 1774354871
    },
    {
      "id": "69c281420000000000e5cdaa",
      "text": "\t損するのあるある[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774354754,
      "updated": 1774355268
    },
    {
      "id": "69c282e00000000000a61f6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774355169,
      "updated": 1774355169
    },
    {
      "id": "69c282e00000000000a61f6e",
      "text": "食べ物を無理やり食べることについて、[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774355169,
      "updated": 1774355290
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2834f0000000000a61f71",
      "text": "\t捨てているに等しいと思うか、",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774355280,
      "updated": 1774355281
    },
    {
      "id": "69c283510000000000a61f72",
      "text": "\t資源の有効活用だと思うか",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774355281,
      "updated": 1774355284
    },
    {
      "id": "69c283540000000000a61f73",
      "text": "\tみたいな話がある[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774355284,
      "updated": 1774355284
    },
    {
      "id": "69c282fe0000000000a61f70",
      "text": " 元を取る話ではないが損失回避の話ではあるか",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774355198,
      "updated": 1774355657
    },
    {
      "id": "69c284320000000000a61f75",
      "text": " 私は無理やり食べるのは嫌いだがゴミに捨てるのは抵抗感がある。",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774355506,
      "updated": 1774355638
    },
    {
      "id": "69c284b60000000000a61f76",
      "text": " \tしかし、残飯をゴミに捨てればQOL低下を防げるので合理的ではありそう。",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774355638,
      "updated": 1774355639
    },
    {
      "id": "69c282e20000000000a61f6f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774355170,
      "updated": 1774355170
    }
  ]
}